{"tid":1880183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[國際] 英國雪菲爾大學學生會鼓勵中國學生舉報香港及台灣學生","createTime":"2020-02-14T15:58:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T17:06:23.000Z","uid":47144,"like":8,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7a3dba1c58c2369fe345f7f7df915be71419ba45","tid":1880183,"uid":47144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T15:58:03.000Z","msg":"2019年8月，國際學生幹事 Sissi Li Mengya 於Wechat&nbsp;<br />\n1. 鼓勵中國學生向官方舉報拒絕自認中國人的台灣及香港人，必須「糾正」<br />\n2. 批評雪菲爾大學不遵守一個中國原則<br />\n3. 外媒關於香港報導係假新聞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n報導：<br />\n<a href=\"http://forgetoday.com/2020/02/12/student-groups-shocked-by-sheffield-su-international-students-officers-pro-china-posts/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforgetoday.com%2F2020%2F02%2F12%2Fstudent-groups-shocked-by-sheffield-su-international-students-officers-pro-china-posts%2F&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNs%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=24b3f455\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://forgetoday.com/2020/02/12/student-groups-shocked-by-sheffield-su-international-students-officers-pro-china-posts/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">RT請煲大中國留學生=共諜=欺壓少數民族</span></strong></span>: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/TheTab/status/1227880933606514688\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTheTab%2Fstatus%2F1227880933606514688&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNs%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=5fe548b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTheTab%2Fstatus%2F1227880933606514688&h=7d599ab7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/TheTab/status/1227880933606514688</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/xinwenxiaojie/status/1228044554181447681\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fxinwenxiaojie%2Fstatus%2F1228044554181447681&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNs%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=17b2ed2e\" 